{"tid":466930,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"(不定期更新)個期鐘意咩歌就推介咩歌","createTime":"2017-11-13T04:29:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T13:29:26.000Z","uid":31716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"93fab671223f112ea8d0b34422e07f650b36b51f","tid":466930,"uid":31716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:29:46.000Z","msg":"睇標題確實係有點隨意,但中英文為主,日韓有但相對少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各位巴絲如果有歌介紹/覺得岩聽歡迎留個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者咁岩聽到歌有感而發都可以分享自己既故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望大家喜歡"},{"pid":"eff280f29232ba9fdfa606ee2161974376b75e90","tid":466930,"uid":31716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:41:24.000Z","msg":"Gin Lee 李幸倪 - 《月球下的人》MV<br />\n近年難得好鐘意既一首廣東歌<br />\n同月球上的人命名相似 主角在月球寂莫難耐觀察地球 <br />\n雖然萬家燈火,但被形容成冰冷感<br />\n「我在月球上俯瞰　一家家吊燈普照是冰冷感」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W73UOP-SVfo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DW73UOP-SVfo&d=K8MRbFANaG7SbqlXmJ27YtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=d56e2cdb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W73UOP-SVfo</a>"},{"pid":"9c673b7f96625ae4ec4acfae92ef260da9a0bae5","tid":466930,"uid":31716,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:51:42.000Z","msg":"Hello Nico〈接下來如何〉官方MV<br />\n第一首可能太多人識所以揀多一首<br />\n呢首歌我好多時會係自己煩腦個陣聽<br />\n做決定之前腦海好多時都會出現'會唔會選擇錯'的問題<br />\n<br />\n愛我的人我還是捨不得 <br />\n捨不得看他痛著 即使被愛得疲倦了<br />\n我愛的人卻變得愛不得 <br />\n愛不得 要怎麼說出我愛上你了<br />\n<br />\n這首歌 是獻給那些做錯決定而後悔的人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iDfZua4IS4A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiDfZua4IS4A&d=K8MRbFANaG7SbqlXmJ27YtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=aed38600\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iDfZua4IS4A</a>"},{"pid":"516cb49f47a20042490baf7a4bbfb4653dd96915","tid":466930,"uid":57594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:07:28.000Z","msg":"湯圓同湯丸？"},{"pid":"6060f071750177a59d251ebf4c66e5264d41724b","tid":466930,"uid":31716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T13:30:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>湯圓同湯丸？</blockquote><br />\n你指第二個女人湯丸?<br />\n我改完個名先知有另一個人係高登改過同一個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b05f829d750f3b02370eb4104398f0080fe013","tid":466930,"uid":31716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:00:48.000Z","msg":"Dido - Life for Rent<br />\n最愛英文歌之一 愛上其歌詞<br />\n個人覺得幾好既歌詞解說:<br />\n<a href=\"http://guanee.blogspot.co.uk/2012/06/life-for-rent.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fguanee.blogspot.co.uk%2F2012%2F06%2Flife-for-rent.html&d=K8MRbFANaG7SbqlXmJ27YtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=9f81550a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://guanee.blogspot.co.uk/2012/06/life-for-rent.html</a><br />\n<br />\n歌名Life for rent意思係指自己人生是「租」回來的<br />\n成首歌每次聽都有困心既感覺，大家不妨留意歌詞感愛下<br />\n<br />\n       But if my life is for rent and I don't learn to buy<br />\n　　Well I deserve nothing more than I get<br />\n　　'cause nothing I have is truly mine<br />\n<br />\n        如果我的人生注定漂泊　<br />\n　　也無法學著怎麼去安定<br />\n　　我擁有的　就只有這麼多<br />\n　　而我所擁有的　卻不真正屬於我<br />\n<br />\n       While my heart is a shield and I won't let it down<br />\n       While I am so afraid to fail so I won't even try<br />\n       Well how can I say I'm alive<br />\n       我的心強烈的防衛着　不容攻破<br />\n       失敗的恐懼　讓我怯於嚐試<br />\n       那麼我還能說我是活著的嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OFtNChII78k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOFtNChII78k&d=K8MRbFANaG7SbqlXmJ27YtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=13f9ad13\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OFtNChII78k</a>"},{"pid":"6684baad08a39b90a1de29cea1b7fec4e4cb364f","tid":466930,"uid":31716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:13:18.000Z","msg":"Coldplay - Fix You<br />\n相信連登呢度好多人都識coldplay同呢首歌<br />\n但in case有人未聽過我覺得點都要係度推介一次<br />\n特別一個人聽個陣真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k4V3Mo61fJM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dk4V3Mo61fJM&d=K8MRbFANaG7SbqlXmJ27YtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=2e35f690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k4V3Mo61fJM</a>"},{"pid":"8046a2f3622e41cb0fef96811d082a5a9d78242e","tid":466930,"uid":31716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:29:26.000Z","msg":"麥浚龍 - 濛<br />\n<br />\n「如果看著我不妨濛一點 .完全望表面或是未完善」<br />\n<br />\n凡事都看得濛一點,不是對大家關係更好嗎...?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hx4Sz05gkzw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dhx4Sz05gkzw&d=K8MRbFANaG7SbqlXmJ27YtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=601204b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hx4Sz05gkzw</a>"}]}